


                    Server Creation - using Express



            1. Create folder for Server

            2. Create package.json -command :npm init

            3. install express(framework)- command : npm i express

            4. create index.js

            5. import express to index.js

            6. create app using express

            7. set port number for Server

            8. To run server : command- node index.js

            9. Resolve API - syntax : express-app.httpMethod(path,callback function)


            10. install nodemon : npm i -g nodemon


            11. JWT token - To validate the user

                1. install jsonwebtoken - npm i jsonwebtoken
                2. import jsonwebtoken

                         11.1 Token Generation - sign({},secretkey)

                         11.2 Token Validate
        
